Question 4: Online Shopping System (Interfaces)
Instructions:
Create a class Product with attributes:

String productID
String productName
double price
int stock
Create an interface CartOperations with methods:

void addToCart(Product product, int quantity): Adds the product to the cart.
void removeFromCart(Product product, int quantity): Removes the product from the cart.
void displayCartDetails(): Displays cart details.
Allow users to:

Add products to the system.
Add or remove products from the cart.
View cart details.

Options:
1. Add Product
2. View Products
3. Add to Cart
4. Remove from Cart
5. View Cart
6. Exit
Choose an option: 1
Enter Product ID: P001
Enter Product Name: Laptop
Enter Price: 1200
Enter Stock: 10
Product added successfully.

Options:
1. Add Product
2. View Products
3. Add to Cart
4. Remove from Cart
5. View Cart
6. Exit
Choose an option: 3
Enter Product ID to add to cart: P001
Enter Quantity: 2
2 units of Laptop added to the cart.

